	 7\n\nTime:\n\n9-11 a.m.\n\nLocation:\n\nEastgate neighborhood\n\nExperien
	ce is not required\, and cleanup supplies will be provided. Come for the f
	ull two hours or drop in and stay as long as you can. Coffee and water wil
	l also be available.\n\nTo register\, visit\n\nCleanEastgate2026.EventBrit
