BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:yFNXBlXE7bEdlM0XB5cCM
SUMMARY:Sturtevant's Ski-Ya-Later Sale: Up to 50% Off Ski and SnowboardGear
DTSTAMP:20260306T004517Z
DTSTART:20260309T170000Z
DESCRIPTION:PNW skiers and snowboarders—spring is the smartest time to upgr
	ade! Sturtevant's (part of Christy Sports) is hosting the annual Ski-Ya-La
	ter Sale from March 6-29\, offering up to 50% off current-season skis\, sn
	owboards\, boots\, bindings\, apparel\, and more—perfect as spring storms 
	bring late-season conditions and families plan ahead during spring break.\
	n\nShop in-person at our Bellevue locations for expert tuning & repair\, c
	ustom boot fitting\, water sports rentals\, and more: Sturtevant's – 13131
	 NE 20th St.\, Bellevue\, WA 98005 (425.869.7669) Hours: Mon-Fri 10 am-7 p
	m\, Sat-Sun 10 am- 6 pm\n\nSturtevant's Ski Mart – 13219 NE 20th St.\, Bel
	levue\, WA 98005 (425.637.8958) Hours: Mon-Fri 10 am-7 pm\, Sat-Sun 10 am-
	6 pm\n\nOr head to Tacoma: Sturtevant's Ski Mart – 2220 So. 37th St.\, Tac
	oma\, WA 98409 (253.473.1134) Hours: Mon-Fri 10 am-7 pm\, Sat-Sun 10 am-6 
	pm.\n\nGreat for families: Stop by for kids' fit checks\, season rental in
	fo\, and early purchases before fall pricing. All discounted items are fin
	al sale\; selection varies by store. Also shop online at christysports.com
	 or sturtevants.com. Upgrade your gear locally this spring—visit Sturtevan
	t's Bellevue or Tacoma today.\n\nDates: March 6 – March 29\, 2026 (Progres
	sive discounts: Up to 30% off March 6-12 with the best selection\; up to 4
