UID:JfUR0Y6xFFF8tQ-IQWVUe
SUMMARY:Sing along 2000
DTSTAMP:20260306T004518Z
DTSTART:20260313T030000Z
DESCRIPTION:Central District (1.9 miles E)\n\nThe Totally 2K Sing Along fea
	tures “hits from 2000 to 2010” on screen with subtitles so you can sing al
	ong to Lady Gaga\, Linkin Park\, Beyoncé\, Justin Bieber\, Missy Elliott\,
	 and Daft Punk at Central Cinema\, 1411 21st Ave. in Seattle. To buy a $17
	 ticket\, click the “tickets” button below\, then “Continue As Guest.”\n\n
	https://central-cinema.com/checkout/showing/the-totally-2k-sing-along/2712
