SUMMARY:Master Gardener Plant Clinic
DTSTAMP:20260306T004518Z
DTSTART:20260314T170000Z
DESCRIPTION:Master Gardeners will be at the Garden to answer your questions
	 on plant selection\, maintenance\, and general gardening\, as well as str
	ategies for managing pest and disease problems. Volunteers provide answers
	\, diagnoses\, and helpful science-based information and resources so you 
	can manage your home landscapes with the most sustainable methods. Feel fr
	ee to bring a bagged sample or photograph for them to review.\n\nhttps://s
	eatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/master-gardener-plant-clinic/16219468
